snippet.title: The Lamplighters League - Gameplay First Look
snippet.description:
Join Harebrained Schemes in this first look at the Lamplighters League, an original pulp adventure set in an alternate 1930s that mixes real-time infiltration, turn-based tactical combat, and managing a growing team of misfits. The Lamplighters League will launch for PC and Xbox Series X and S consoles in 2023.

Wishlist Now: https://pdxint.at/PdxLamplightersLeague
